Not much to read right now!

DEPENDENCIES:
---------------------------------------------
 * Recent versions of cdrkit (genisoimage and wodim)
 * Recent versions of dvd+rw-tools 
 * Python (>=2.6.2)
 * wxpython (>=2.8.9) (Note: The package is called python-wxgtk in Ubuntu, etc)
 * Libnotify binaries (OPTIONAL) 

To Run
---------------------------------------------

Decompress the tarball.
Change directory (cd in terminal) to the directory 'yagoburn'.
Type : 'python yagoburn.py' and press ENTER.
OR (if in GUI filemanager) just double click on file yagoburn.py

